stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR
    [*] --> Stable
    Stable: Stable\nlag < 50ms
    Elevated: Elevated\nlag 50-200ms
    Critical: Critical\nlag > 200ms

    Stable --> Elevated: lag rises above 50ms
    Elevated --> Critical: lag rises above 200ms
    Elevated --> Stable: lag drops below 50ms
    Critical --> Elevated: lag drops below 200ms
